query:
SELECT 
    LOWER(TRIM(nome)) as nome_norm,
    data_nascimento,
    COUNT(*) as qtd,
    GROUP_CONCAT(id_paciente ORDER BY created_at SEPARATOR ', ') as ids
FROM pacientes 
WHERE deleted_at IS NULL 
    AND data_nascimento IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY LOWER(TRIM(nome)), data_nascimento
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
ORDER BY qtd DESC, nome_norm
LIMIT 100;
